# Verzephronix Project Structure

This Flutter app follows a modular architecture with clear separation of concerns:

- `lib/main.dart` is the entry point
- `lib/app.dart` defines the main app structure and navigation
- Core features are organized in separate directories:
  - `lib/group_generator/` - Group generation feature
  - `lib/match_scorer/` - Match scoring feature
  - `lib/led_scroller/` - LED scrolling display feature
  - `lib/settings/` - App settings and preferences
- Shared utilities are in `lib/utils/`
- Reusable widgets are in `lib/widgets/`

Each feature module follows a consistent pattern with screen, controller, and model files.